                            (“Qualifying Bet”),</li>
                        <li>Any bets placed on the Qualifying Games during the Promotion Period which resulted in a win
                            or loss will count towards the Qualifying Bet. Free spins, cancelled or void bets or bets
                            placed in "Play for Fun" mode during the Promotion Period will not count towards the
                            Qualifying Bet.</li>
